short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to rewrite text using OpenAI API and translate to Austrian dialects via AI.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Servus! Have you ever wanted to turn your text into proper Wienerisch? With the Austrian AI Chrome Extension, now you can! Harnessing the power of OpenAI's cutting-edge AI technology, we're bringing a bit of Austrian charm to your browser. It's truly a wonder, isn't it?
